title: June - Outdoor-Floor and Table lamps
description:
Designed by the Emiliana Design Studio for Vibia the June floor lamp collection is characterised by its ability to create ambiences filled with life where light and people interact generating warm atmospheres. The June collection is perfect for exterior spaces thanks to its IP65 rating.
 
June lanterns can be installed externally, either built-in or surface mounted. June comes in a natural colour palette, matt lacquered dark brown. This collection is ideal for the outdoors, to illuminate and highlight paths and walkways as well as large open spaces. All the elements feature LED light sources.
